            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">A little background about where all started</h5>
                    <p></p>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        As I grew up, I always heard the phrase "Every cup of coffee tells a story". Back then, when I was around 5 or 6 years old, I always wondered: how could a cup of coffee tell such thing?
                        And my mom kinldly answared "A cup of coffee has super powers, darling, that not everybody knows about. When we sit down at a cute small table, while sipping coffee, we tell stories and
                        the coffee cup listens to them carefuly and memorises every detail. So, when the time is up, we go to work and next time when we catch up, the coffe cupe will tell us right where we left
