    <div class="card text-white bg-primary mb-3" style="padding:10px">
        <div class="card-header">After I grew up, I realised that...</div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p></p>
            <p class="card-text">
                When people gather over a cup of coffee, they often engage in conversation and share their thoughts, feelings, and experiences. 
                These conversations can be light-hearted or serious, and they can involve sharing stories about personal experiences, discussing 
                current events, or even brainstorming ideas.
                </br><p></p>
                Through these conversations, a sense of community and connection can be built, and the shared experiences can create lasting memories. 
                And while the coffee cup itself may not have superpowers, it can serve as a symbol of the shared experience and the memories that were 
                created during that time.
                </br><p></p>
                So, while a cup of coffee may not actually listen and remember everything that is said during a conversation, it can still serve as a 
                meaningful part of the experience and contribute to the storytelling that takes place.
            </p>
        </div>

